Message.Jp: 白翼覚者隊・納品依頼　ハイデル平原

Message.En:
Notice from the Temple to the Arisen
stationed locally. Please deliver 
<LQVA> <LQIM> 
obtained from your location to the Temple.
We are currently low on supplies, 
so any assistance is humbly requested.
